question: What is the encounter associated with the immunization Influenza  seasonal  injectable  preservative free?
answers:
[Q]: Retrieve all patients who have been prescribed a Flu vaccine.
[SPARQL]: 
```sparql
PREFIX snomed: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#snomed:SNOMED-CT>
PREFIX loinc: <https://knacc.umbc.edu/dae-young/kim/ontologies/synthea#loinc:LOINC>
SELECT DISTINCT ?first ?last
WHERE {
  ?subject a syn:Patient;
  syn:first ?first;
  syn:last ?last;
  syn:hasMedicationPrescription ?prescription.
  ?prescription syn:performer ?performer.
  ?performer a syn:Practitioner.
  ?prescription syn:medicationOrderingProvider ?orderingProvider.
  ?orderingProvider a syn:Practitioner.
  ?prescription syn:status "completed".
  ?prescription syn:medication ?medication.
  ?medication a syn:Medication;
  syn:medicationCode ?medicationCode.
  ?medicationCode snomed:equivalentTo ?equivalentMedicationCode.
  ?equivalentMedicationCode loinc:description ?loincDescription.
  ?loincDescription pl:value ?loincValue.
  FILTER ( ?loincValue = "Influenza vaccine" )
}
```
